Subject: Still Interested in the [job_title] Role? Let's Connect!

Body:
<html>
<body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;margin:0;padding:0;">
<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Hi [applicant_first_name],</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">I hope you're doing well. We wanted to check in and see if you're still interested in the <strong style="font-weight:700">[job_title]</strong> role with Outsourced Pro Global.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Your application caught our attention, and we believe your skills and experience align well with what we're looking for. We're excited about the possibility of you joining our team.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">If you'd like to move forward, simply schedule an interview at a time that works best for you using the link below:</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><a href="[Schedule Your Interview Here]" style="display:inline-block;background-color:#0057b8;color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.38;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;">Schedule Your Interview</a></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Should you have any concerns or questions, please email, call, or text your Recruitment Specialist: <strong style="font-weight:700">[recruiter_phone_line]</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Thank you for considering Outsourced Pro Global as your next career step. We look forward to connecting with you soon.</span></span></p>

[signature]
</body>
</html>
